 /* 
  *  BUTTONS:
  *  UP:      light RED(RGB) LED 
  *  DOWN:    light BLUE(RGB) LED
  *  LEFT:    light BLUE LED
  *  RIGHT:   make some noise (buzzer)
  *  CENTER:  light GREEN(RGB) LED
  *  
  * ADDRESSABLE LEDs (WS2812):
  *   [0] - random color
  *   [1-4] - PCB backlight (BLUE)
  */
  
